</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>中國政府打擊虛擬貨幣挖礦     360 開發監控系統協助收集數據</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/02/360-threat-situation-monitoring-system-launched-the-mining-monitoring-function-and-monitored-the-daily-ip-activity-of-mining-host-109000-in-november/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=360-threat-situation-monitoring-system-launched-the-mining-monitoring-function-and-monitored-the-daily-ip-activity-of-mining-host-109000-in-november</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 02 Dec 2021 11:17:34 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[360]]></category><category><![CDATA[中國]]></category><category><![CDATA[挖礦]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1073935</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>中國政府近日大力打擊虛擬貨幣「挖礦」活動，為配合多個部門實行監管，中國境內知名網絡安全公司 360 集團開發了 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">中國政府近日大力打擊虛擬貨幣「挖礦」活動，為配合多個部門實行監管，中國境內知名網絡安全公司 360 集團開發了一套監控系統，以協助政府收集挖礦數據，用以支持後續的整治工作。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1073937" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/7B8114B3-F9D7-468D-92F9-2CDD56F1A945.jpeg" alt="" width="556" height="233" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">中國國家發展改革委會、中央宣傳部、中央網信辨、工信部等部門，日前聯合發佈了《關於整治虛擬貨幣「挖礦」活動的通知》，公佈各省區市要落實做好「挖礦」的整治工作。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1073938" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DF1F5342-4F79-4389-A3B6-240C86AE5579.png" alt="" width="600" height="495" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">據中國媒體引述，360 政企安全集團基於大數據、知識庫和技術分析能力，構建了一套「360 威脅態勢監控系統」。一方面通過基於地理區域（省/市/區縣）、網絡類型（數據中心、企業專線）等進行宏觀態勢統計監測，幫助監管用戶了解轄區「挖礦」態勢。另一方面基於「挖礦」整治需要，360 將直接輸出挖礦主機清單，清單內容包含涉及單位的挖礦主機的 IP 地址、地理位置、網絡類型、連接頻率、處置建議等信息，直接交予監管部門，繼而進行後續的工作。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">根據 11 月的監測數據顯示，中國全國日均挖礦主機 IP 活躍量有 10.9 萬個，主要分佈在廣東省、江蘇省、浙江省及山東省。這些主機除了使用企業專線進行挖礦工作外，還有使用家庭用的寬頻去「挖礦」。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://360.net/about/news/article61a6e736eec939004a2dfb09">360 政企安全</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=pFsn2QbtCgA:M7cmudjHuEs:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=pFsn2QbtCgA:M7cmudjHuEs:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>中國 iPhone 盲盒網民解拆     2013 年處理器 + 不能上 App Store</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/02/iphone-2013/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=iphone-2013</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 02 Dec 2021 10:11:35 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone]]></category><category><![CDATA[盲盒]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1073827</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>抽盲盒風氣於中國盛行，自助盲盒機於當地隨處可見。有不少商人以貴價商品作招徠，例如名牌化妝品及電子產品等，吸引不 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>抽盲盒風氣於中國盛行，自助盲盒機於當地隨處可見。有不少商人以貴價商品作招徠，例如名牌化妝品及電子產品等，吸引不少人購買盲盒。近日有中國網民抽到裝有 iPhone 的盲盒，包裝與正版無異，但排線卻印有中文，甚至使用 2013 年的聯發科處理器。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.27.56.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073874" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.27.56-694x370.png" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.27.56-694x370.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.27.56-1280x682.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.27.56-768x409.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.27.56-1536x819.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.27.56-2048x1092.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.27.56.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.23.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073875" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.23-694x370.png" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.23-694x370.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.23-1280x682.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.23-768x409.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.23-1536x819.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.23-2048x1092.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.23.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>該 iPhone 的包裝外盒與正版的十分相似，亦有清楚列明型號及容量大，而電話實物的外觀像真度亦很高，不過一看到機背的鏡頭便知是假冒貨。機背的三鏡頭與正版比明顯較小，而且有點反光。電話的介面與正版 iOS 一致，但反應速度緩慢，不過現時不少應用程式皆能把 Android 介面轉成翻版 iOS。 按電話設定頁面顯示，該手機稱為 iPhone 11 Pro Max，亦有清楚列明型號號碼及序列號，惟不能連接 App Store。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.36.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073876" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.36-694x370.png" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.36-694x370.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.36-1280x682.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.36-768x409.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.36-1536x819.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.36-2048x1092.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.36.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.51.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073878" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.51-694x370.png" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.51-694x370.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.51-1280x682.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.51-768x409.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.51-1536x819.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.51-2048x1092.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.28.51.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.29.02.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073879" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.29.02-694x370.png" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.29.02-694x370.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.29.02-1280x682.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.29.02-768x409.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.29.02-1536x819.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.29.02-2048x1092.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.29.02.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.29.20.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073880" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.29.20-694x370.png" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-下午 4.2